Package org.glassfish.jersey.server.model

Interface Consuming

All Known Implementing Classes:
ResourceMethod
public interface Consuming
Model component that is able to consume media types. A component implementing this interface provides additional information about the supported consumed media types.
Author:
Jakub Podlesak, Marek Potociar
